<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَوْسُ بنُ حَجَرٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - وَعِنْدِي قُرُوضُ الْخَيْرِ وَالشَّرِّ مِثْلُهُ ... فَبُؤْسَى لَدَى بؤْسَى ونُعَمَى لأنْعُمِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٨٥٩)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ كُثَيِّرُ بنُ عَبْدِ الرحْمنِ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - هُوَ الْمَرْءُ يَجْزِي بالْكَرَامَةِ أَهْلَهَا ... وَيَحْذُو بِنَعْلِ الْمُسْتَثِيبِ مِثَالَهَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨٦٠)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ هُبَيْرَةُ بنُ مُسَاحِقٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - جَزَيْت بمثْلِ قَرْضِهِمَ عُقَيْلًا ... سَوَاءً مِثْلَ صَاعِهمِ الْمَكيلِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٨٦١)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الْوَلِيدُ بنُ يَزِيدٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١ - وَإِنَّ عَلَى شَاطِي الْفُرَاتِ لَفِتْيَةً ... يَوَدُّونَ لَوْ كَانُوا بِمَالِهِمِ افْتَدَوْا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٢ - حَدَوْنَا وَسَاقُونا فَنَحْنُ كمَا تَرَى ... نَسُوقُ كَمَا سَاقُوا وَنَحْدُوا كَمَا حَدَوْا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٨٦٢)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَدِيُّ بنُ زَيْدٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>